文本​统计​：​约​ 2169 ​个​字​  •  41 ​行​代码​  ​预计​阅读​时间​ 8 ​分钟​  <p>​从​一个​可行​解​开始​，​我们​在​它​的​邻域​内​寻找​更好​的​解​，​如果​邻域​内​没有​更好​的​解​了​，​那么​我们​就​称​这个​解是​一个​ local optimum (​局部​最优​解​)</p> <p>​我们​的​算法​大纲​如下​，​找到​邻域​，cost(S) ​以及​从​S​到​S’​的​方法​</p> <pre><code>SolutionType Gradient_descent()
{   Start from a feasible solution S in FS ;
MinCost = cost(S);
while (1) {
S’ = Search( N(S) ); /* find the best S’ in N(S) */
CurrentCost = cost(S’);
if ( CurrentCost &lt; MinCost ) {
MinCost = CurrentCost;    S = S’;
}
else  break;
}
return S;
}
</code></pre>

文本​统计​：​约​ 930 ​个​字​  ​预计​阅读​时间​ 3 ​分钟​  <p>​根据​前​几章​的​内容​，​我们​得到​了​以下​公式​</p> <p>​在​真空​中​，​我们​有​</p> \[  egin{aligned} &amp;​电场​高斯​定律​：\iint_{​闭合​曲面​}\vec E \cdot d\vec A= rac{q_0}{\epsilon_0}\ &amp;​磁场​高斯​定律​：\iint_{​闭合​曲面​}\vec B \cdot d\vec A=0\ &amp;​法拉第​电磁感应​定律​：\oint\vec E\cdot d\vec l=- rac{d\Phi_B}{dt}=-\iint rac{\partial \vec B}{\partial t}\cdot d\vec A\ &amp;​安培​环路​定律​：\oint\vec B\cdot d\vec l=\mu_0i \end{aligned} \] <p>​在​电介质​和​磁介质​中​，</p> \[ \left\{   egin{aligned} &amp;\iint_{​闭合​曲面​}\vec D \cdot d\vec A=q_0\ &amp;\iint_{​闭合​曲面​}\vec B \cdot d\vec A=0\ &amp;\oint\vec E\cdot d\vec l=- rac{d\Phi_B}{dt}=-\iint rac{\partial \vec B}{\partial t}\cdot d\vec A\ &amp;\oint\vec H\cdot d\vec l=i=\iint\vec j\cdot d\vec A \end{aligned}ight. \] <p>​微分形式​：</p> \[ \left\{  egin{aligned} &amp;
abla\cdot \vec D=ho_{e0}\ &amp;
abla\cdot \vec B=0\ &amp;
abla	imes \vec E=- rac{\partial \vec B}{\partial t}\ &amp;
abla 	imes \vec H=\vec j_0 \end{aligned} ight. \] <p>​既然​变化​的​磁场​会​产生​涡旋​电场​，​那么​变化​的​电场​是否​会​产生​相应​的​磁场​呢​？​上述​公式​在​面对​非​恒定电流​的​情况​时​，​出现​了​矛盾​，​于是​麦克斯韦​提出​了​”​位移电流​“​的​假设​。</p> <p>​在​非​恒定电流​条件​下​，\(\iint_{​闭合​曲面​S}j_0\cdot dS=- rac{dq_0}{dt}\)，​这里​的​ \(q_0\) ​就是​积累​在​S​面内​的​自由电荷​。</p> <p>​根据​ \(\iint_{​闭合​曲面​}\vec D \cdot d\vec S=q_0\)，​可​得​ \( rac{dq_0}{dt}= rac{d}{dt}\iint_{​闭合​曲面​}\vec D \cdot d\vec S=\iint_{​闭合​曲面​} rac{\partial D}{\partial t}\cdot dS\)</p> <p>​从而​我们​可以​得到​ \(\iint_{​闭合​曲面​}(j_0+ rac{\partial D}{\partial t})\cdot dS=0\)</p> <p>​我们​称​ \(\Phi_D=\iint\vec D\cdot d\vec S\) ​为​电位移​通量​，\(i_D= rac{\Phi D}{dt}=-\iint rac{\partial D}{\partial t}\cdot dS\) ​称为​位移电流​，\(\vec j_D= rac{\partial D}{\partial t}\) ​称为​ ​位移电流​密度​。</p> <p>​以​电容器​为​例来​理解​全​电流​（\(i_0+i_D\)) ​是​连续​的​</p> <p>Example</p> <p></p> <p>​在​一个​极板​的​内外​两侧​各作​一面​\(S_1\)​和​\(S_2\), ​通过​前者​的​有​传导电流​也​有​位移电流​，​后者​则​只有​位移电流​ ​通过​\(S_1\)​的​全​电流​为​</p> \[     (j_0+ rac{\partial D_​内​}{\partial t})S=j_0S=I_0 \] <p>​通过​\(S_2\)​的​全​电流​为​</p> \[  rac{\Phi_D}{dt}= rac{\partial D_​外​}{\partial t}S= rac{\partial \sigma_{e0}}{\partial t}S \] <p>​而​\(j_0= rac{\partial \sigma_{e0}}{\partial t}\),​从而​可​得​上述​两个​式子​相等​</p> <p>​在​真空​中​我们​可以​得到​电容器​内部​变化​的​电场​产生​涡旋​磁场​的​公式​为​</p> \[  egin{aligned} &amp;\oint\vec H\cdot d\vec l=\iint rac{\partial \vec D}{\partial t}\cdot d\vec A\ &amp;\oint rac{\vec B}{\mu_0}\cdot d\vec l=\iint\epsilon_0 rac{\partial \vec E}{\partial t}\cdot d\vec A\ &amp;\oint\vec B\cdot d\vec l=\mu_0\epsilon_0\iint rac{\partial \vec E}{\partial t}\cdot d\vec A\ \end{aligned} \] <p>Example</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>​由​上述​内容​，​我们​得到​新​的​安培​环路​定律​ \(\oint\vec H\cdot d\vec l=i_0+i_D=\iint(\vec j_0+ rac{\partial \vec D}{\partial t})\cdot d\vec A\)</p> <p>​进而​我们​得到​麦克斯韦​方程组​</p> \[ \left\{   egin{aligned} &amp;\iint_{​闭合​曲面​}\vec D \cdot d\vec A=q_0\ &amp;\iint_{​闭合​曲面​}\vec B \cdot d\vec A=0\ &amp;\oint\vec E\cdot d\vec l=- rac{d\Phi_B}{dt}=-\iint rac{\partial \vec B}{\partial t}\cdot d\vec A\ &amp;\oint\vec H\cdot d\vec l=\iint(\vec j_0+ rac{\partial \vec D}{\partial t})\cdot d\vec A=I_0+\iint rac{\partial \vec D}{\partial t}\cdot d\vec A \end{aligned}ight. \] <p>​微分形式​</p> \[ \left\{  egin{aligned} &amp;
abla\cdot \vec D=ho_{e0}\ &amp;
abla\cdot \vec B=0\ &amp;
abla	imes \vec E=- rac{\partial \vec B}{\partial t}\ &amp;
abla 	imes \vec H=\vec j_0+ rac{\partial \vec D}{\partial t} \end{aligned} ight. \] <p>​如果​我们​存在​磁单极子​，​那么​麦克斯韦​方程​就​具有​完全​的​对称性​了​。</p> <p>Cavity Oscillations (​谐振腔​)</p> <p></p> <p>​变化​的​电场​产生​磁场​，​变化​的​磁场​产生​电场​。</p> <p></p>
